item.title: Rolling and Static Forward PER Bands
item.description: # Rolling average of blended forward estimates (1BF) bf1.rolling <- per1 %>% filter( year(Date) >= (last.5yrs-5) ) %>% select(Date, psei) %>% gather(key, value, -Date) %>% mutate( value = replace(value, value == "#N/A N/A", NA) %>% as.numeric() ) %>% group_by(key) %>% mutate( rolling.avg = rollapplyr(value, FUN = mean, width = 252 * 5, na.rm = TRUE, fill = NA), rolling.sd = rollapplyr(value, FUN = sd, width = 252 * 5, na.
